Caption: On the left Prof. B. Sengupto speaking at the Convocation. The Registrar of IIT Madras Mr. R. Natarajan is seen addressing the audience at the Convocation.
Description: On the dais sitting from left: Mr. M.C. Chagla, Dr. A.L. Mudaliar, xxx, Dr. Y. Nayudamma, Prof. Venkat Rao, Prof. Klein, Prof. P.C. Varghese and Prof. Lutz. Natarajan would proceed to retire from his post in the same month. His farewell party was held two days before the Second Convocation (1st April 1965). He officially retired on the 6th of April.
